The Block Australia Fans vs Faves Series 8 Episode 25

The Block is back with a Fans versus Favorites format - will the old hands prevail?

It's a Block wedding when 2012 contestants Brad and Lara get married. Everyone enjoys a night off from renovating followed by a leisurely lunch with Scotty. But he and Shelley have a surprise challenge and its fans versus faves.
